name: CAPTAIN ABEARICA #109 [Textless]
description:
Origin retold of Captain Abearica (Bear Rogers) "The Bearo That Was!" - Bear Rogers thinks back to one of his last missions with Bearky, and relays the tale of how he came to be Captain Abearica to Bear Fury.

Enjoy this Commemorative coin of the Textless cover of CAPTAIN ABEARICA #109!
